-- Rio says BHP proposal "well out of ballpark"
-- 
-- Sun Nov 11, 2007 10:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/12/us-riotinto-bhpbilliton-response-idUSSYU00347920071112

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - Rio Tinto Ltd/Plc ( RIO.AX ) said a takeover proposal by rival BHP Billiton Ltd/Plc <BHP.AX remains "well out of the ballpark." 

 A company spokesman said BHP's three-shares-for-one proposal for Rio, worth around $139 billion, significantly undervalued Rio and its propsects.